    "description_long": "This object consists of two adjacent rectangular grave plots, each with a raised stone base and an upright headstone at one end. The headstones are simple, rectangular slabs, each featuring a prominent black Latin cross inlaid or painted on the left side. The stone surfaces have a gray, slightly mottled texture, suggesting a granite or concrete material. The graves are set on a larger rectangular platform, providing a stable foundation and a clean, geometric appearance. There are no visible inscriptions or decorative elements aside from the crosses, giving the graves a minimalist and somber aesthetic.",
